Gaster usually a little shorter than mesosoma (
Fig. 82
); petiole long, 4.5–5.0x as long as wide, smooth, 1.3–1.4x as long as metacoxa; ovipositor occupying 0.7–0.8x length of gaster, barely or a just little exserted beyond apex of gaster (by at most 0.1x own length), 0.6–0.7x length of metatibia.

